snippet.title: DJMAX RAY for iOS Teaser Movie
snippet.description:
NAME IS OFFICIAL.
Coming Soon This Fall on iOS. Worldwide Release on Korea, Japan, and US via App Store.
This game will be the port or sequel to the DJMAX Portable series.
Also, Pentavision (or NEOWIZ Mobile) challenged users to guess the name of this game. The full name is "DJMAX ???". Guess that 3 letters!
